{
  "texts": [
    "Removing the Planner reduces MA-RAG to a single-turn RAG system with document filtering but no query decomposition.",
    "While it still performs well on simpler, single-hop datasets, it struggles with multi-hop questions requiring structured reasoning.",
    "The largest performance drop occurs on multi-hop datasets, emphasizing the Planner's importance in guiding complex reasoning.",
    "These results show both agents are essential: the Extractor enhances precision, and the Planner enables effective reasoning across diverse question types.",
    "Impact of LLMs."
  ]
}